285
00:13:52,919 --> 00:13:54,400
We were worried that

286
00:13:54,400 --> 00:13:56,039
he could not wake up before.

287
00:13:56,200 --> 00:13:57,719
But he's awake now.

288
00:13:58,000 --> 00:13:59,960
So, we should be more confident now.

289
00:14:00,719 --> 00:14:01,799
As long as he's not well,

290
00:14:02,039 --> 00:14:03,400
