341
00:16:09,719 --> 00:16:10,719
I don't get it.

342
00:16:11,719 --> 00:16:12,880
I'm just like you.

343
00:16:13,039 --> 00:16:14,440
Didn't you take all
the responsibilities on your own?

344
00:16:15,760 --> 00:16:16,280
How do you know that?

345
00:16:16,280 --> 00:16:17,840
Come out. It's time for exercise.

346
00:16:19,479 --> 00:16:21,479
