355
00:17:06,199 --> 00:17:06,760
Let's go.

356
00:17:37,800 --> 00:17:38,599
Mr. Lei.

357
00:17:39,719 --> 00:17:40,520
Mr. Lei.

358
00:17:40,640 --> 00:17:41,520
Guys.

359
00:17:43,920 --> 00:17:44,680
