368
00:17:56,719 --> 00:17:58,040
I'll make you some tea.

369
00:17:58,040 --> 00:17:58,920
Go ahead.

370
00:18:01,520 --> 00:18:04,119
Mr. Lei, I'm Lin Xiangyuan.

371
00:18:04,599 --> 00:18:05,719
Do you still remember?

372
00:18:12,800 --> 00:18:13,640
Mr. Lei,

373
00:18:13,839 --> 00:18:15,520
