416
00:19:49,880 --> 00:19:50,640
It's fine. It's fine.

417
00:19:50,640 --> 00:19:52,079
Yuzheng, they are all bad guys.

418
00:19:52,400 --> 00:19:53,439
They're guests.

419
00:19:53,719 --> 00:19:54,880
You're bad, too.

420
00:19:54,920 --> 00:19:56,719
Bad guy. Back off!

421
00:19:56,719 --> 00:19:57,199
Look!

422
00:19:57,199 --> 00:19:58,079
Back off! All of you!

423
00:19:58,439 --> 00:19:59,160
Good lord.

424
00:19:59,319 --> 00:20:00,839
