425
00:20:01,479 --> 00:20:03,520
He's out of his mind sometimes.

426
00:20:03,760 --> 00:20:05,760
Let's make it another day, shall we?

427
00:20:06,359 --> 00:20:07,199
Fine.

428
00:20:07,719 --> 00:20:08,479
Ask them to leave!

429
00:20:08,920 --> 00:20:10,479
They 're gone.

430
00:20:10,640 --> 00:20:11,920
Excuse me.

431
00:20:14,520 --> 00:20:16,800
