432
00:20:22,319 --> 00:20:24,079
It's bloody hell out of luck.

433
00:20:24,239 --> 00:20:25,359
Got beaten for nothing.

434
00:20:25,520 --> 00:20:26,680
He is out of your mind, isn't he?

435
00:20:26,800 --> 00:20:28,400
Why is it so easy for him to get angry?

436
00:20:28,520 --> 00:20:29,280
Never mind.

437
00:20:30,400 --> 00:20:31,800
There is no need
to take offence at a patient.

438
00:20:32,160 --> 00:20:33,199
Let him take it out.

439
00:20:33,719 --> 00:20:34,719
Just consider it as

440
00:20:35,880 --> 00:20:37,160
an apology I make to him.

441
00:20:38,640 --> 00:20:40,040
Now Lei Yuzheng is in jail.

442
00:20:40,599 --> 00:20:42,280
He is so sick.

443
00:20:44,920 --> 00:20:46,479
Yutian shall count on me.

444
00:20:46,760 --> 00:20:47,880
That's true.

445
00:20:48,079 --> 00:20:50,920
You're the manager
of Yutian from now on.

446
00:20:52,359 --> 00:20:55,079
